{"tid":697272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本擬在石垣島部署反艦導彈 射程已涵蓋台灣","createTime":"2018-06-11T00:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T17:10:11.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86f776a185e5c6a048e63f85484ec471f82e6ddc","tid":697272,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"日本擬在石垣島部署反艦導彈 射程已涵蓋台灣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2454118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2454118&d=l9VKxDsGp6iGW%2FHX6EPx8E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e3262227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2454118&h=58459be0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2454118</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕根據軍事新聞網站「Alert5」報導，日本正在計畫，開發一個更長距離的「反艦飛彈」，初步部署在日本沖繩縣，該網站研判，導彈涵蓋範圍包括台灣東北部。<br />\n<br />\n「Alert5」引述《讀賣新聞》的訊息指出，該款新型導彈射程，是現有的第二型地對艦導彈100公里的3倍，該款導彈若部署在石垣島上，涵蓋範圍包含了台灣部分地區，包括台北都在射程範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n根據報導內容，若射程達300公里，台灣東北部海域、陸域都在導彈射程範圍內，我在東北部海域活動的艦艇也受威脅。報導認為，新武器將使日本能夠為有爭議的尖閣群島辯護。<br />\n<br />\n英國《獨立報》今年2月曾報導，稱日本正在強化石垣島作為前線的作戰能力，當時提到日本將部署美製MIM-104愛國者飛彈、SSM-1反艦飛彈等武器，以及600名官兵已經陸續進駐該島。"},{"pid":"847fc5bb0c9d70ea030afe9616056307f16f8e23","tid":697272,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"中國移回南海飛彈系統<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1208245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1208245&d=l9VKxDsGp6iGW%2FHX6EPx8E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c674285c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1208245&h=713ac450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1208245</a><br />\n<br />\n正值美國與中國在南海激烈角力的敏感時刻，以色列情報分析公司「國際衛星影像公司」十一日指出，中國部署在南海西沙群島永興島上的飛彈系統，三日才顯示有部分設施不見蹤影，八日拍攝的最新空拍照卻再次出現被撤離的飛彈系統。分析指出，中國此前撤離飛彈，可能是為了緩解與美國之間的緊張情勢。也<span style=\"color: red;\">有專家指出，中國可能是因飛彈系統不適合當地環境，或受到鹹水損傷，暫時性移除部份設備進行修繕、替換。</span>（編譯劉宜庭）"},{"pid":"308444d809facc4b48d63e3e90d92237e1db60db","tid":697272,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fed58eca32507447a1b1327b00bab2478d02b19","tid":697272,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"射啊射射支那"},{"pid":"1890aedebdbe54a6ed59135fa076c092e0f8271a","tid":697272,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe28b85f30fa50daee76c5292c8564f11b85a38","tid":697272,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"咁又唔係射台仔既<br />\n<br />\n一旦開戰, 日本仲要幫美帝去協防你台灣啦, <br />\n<br />\n你台灣自己都顧唔掂自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f2dc02c9205853f0023602ba987ea57da0b649","tid":697272,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebe28b85f30fa50daee76c5292c8564f11b85a38","tid":697272,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"咁又唔係射台仔既<br />\n<br />\n一旦開戰, 日本仲要幫美帝去協防你台灣啦, <br />\n<br />\n你台灣自己都顧唔掂自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8_KyekhXo9.eoO1wWv83ZA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDEyO2g9MzU0/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/f64296031c9c8dd7a14d109be1948837\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8_KyekhXo9.eoO1wWv83ZA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDEyO2g9MzU0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.